-[grunt]
-[scream]

00:07:28.582 --> 00:07:31.152 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Team Hanawa</i>
 <i>regains control of the ball.</i>

00:07:31.185 --> 00:07:32.720 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Masao]
Hiroshi, pass it here.

00:07:32.753 --> 00:07:33.521 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:33.554 --> 00:07:34.555 position:21% line:89% align:start
[reac] Are you sure?

00:07:34.588 --> 00:07:36.090 position:27% line:83% align:start
You guys can't do
the Hurricane.

00:07:36.123 --> 00:07:37.758 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just do as I tell you.

00:07:37.792 --> 00:07:39.727 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Now Masao</i>
 <i>has the ball.</i>

00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:40.795 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:40.828 --> 00:07:43.496 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But he's the only</i>
 <i>one who can attack.</i>

00:07:43.531 --> 00:07:44.765 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Masao]
 <i>Now, Kazuo.</i>

00:07:44.799 --> 00:07:45.666 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Kazuo]
 <i>Brother, don't tell me</i>

00:07:45.700 --> 00:07:47.335 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>you want to try it again.</i>

00:07:47.368 --> 00:07:48.669 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Masao]
 <i>It's our last opportunity</i>

00:07:48.703 --> 00:07:50.972 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to beat Nankatsu</i>
 <i>once and for all.</i>

00:07:51.005 --> 00:07:52.873 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>We have to do it, Kazuo.</i>

00:07:52.907 --> 00:07:53.975 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Ready?!</i>

00:07:54.008 --> 00:07:55.242 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:07:55.276 --> 00:07:57.511 position:27% line:83% align:start
They have another
special move?

00:07:58.512 --> 00:08:01.481 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Masao kicks</i>
 <i>the ball into the air.</i>

00:08:01.515 --> 00:08:03.451 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And Kazuo runs directly</i>
 <i>towards it.</i>

00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:04.685 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>What are they up to?</i>

00:08:04.719 --> 00:08:07.088 position:13% line:83% align:start
We are the best soccer duo
in all of Japan.

00:08:07.121 --> 00:08:10.257 position:10% line:83% align:start
And now we'll show it to you
with our special shot.

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:13.828 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's impossible.

00:08:13.861 --> 00:08:17.231 position:19% line:83% align:start
-This is our Twin Shot!
-This is our Twin Shot!

00:08:18.566 --> 00:08:19.433 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Incredible!</i>

00:08:19.467 --> 00:08:20.634 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>The Tachibana Twins</i>

00:08:20.668 --> 00:08:22.870 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>shoot at the same time.</i>
-Uhh... [scream]

00:08:22.903 --> 00:08:24.405 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yuzo]
 <i>There's just one ball,</i>

00:08:24.438 --> 00:08:25.873 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>and that ball...</i>

00:08:25.906 --> 00:08:27.441 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>is my friend.</i>

00:08:27.475 --> 00:08:28.542 position:24% line:89% align:start
Like a good friend,

00:08:28.576 --> 00:08:30.177 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'll receive it
with open arms.

00:08:30.211 --> 00:08:31.278 position:38% line:89% align:start
Morisaki!

00:08:31.312 --> 00:08:32.713 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>The ball hits</i>

00:08:32.747 --> 00:08:34.782 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>the goalkeeper</i>
 <i>Morisaki's shoulder.</i>

00:08:34.815 --> 00:08:35.850 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:35.883 --> 00:08:38.052 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But the ball is</i>
 <i>still spinning towards</i>

00:08:38.085 --> 00:08:39.520 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>the corner of the goal.</i>

00:08:39.553 --> 00:08:40.688 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Go inside.
-No!

00:08:40.721 --> 00:08:42.790 position:35% line:83% align:start
Dammit all.
If they score now,

00:08:42.823 --> 00:08:44.425 position:30% line:83% align:start
we'll be out of
the tournament.

00:08:44.458 --> 00:08:47.561 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:08:48.462 --> 00:08:50.598 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Izhizaki</i>
 <i>from Team Nankatsu</i>

00:08:50.631 --> 00:08:51.632 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>deflects the ball</i>

00:08:51.665 --> 00:08:53.134 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>by putting</i>
 <i>his body in danger.</i>

00:08:53.167 --> 00:08:53.968 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:08:54.001 --> 00:08:55.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
-That's it, Ishizaki!
-[laughs]

00:08:55.536 --> 00:08:56.804 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's what I call defense,
buddy!

00:08:56.837 --> 00:08:57.972 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:08:58.005 --> 00:08:59.840 position:44% line:83% align:start
-No!
-Ishizaki!

00:08:59.874 --> 00:09:02.511 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Now Tsubasa</i>
 <i>has possession of the ball.</i>

00:09:02.543 --> 00:09:03.677 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ishizaki...

00:09:03.711 --> 00:09:05.679 position:16% line:83% align:start
What are you waiting for,
Tsubasa?

00:09:05.713 --> 00:09:07.615 position:19% line:83% align:start
They don't have anyone
defending right now.

00:09:07.648 --> 00:09:09.984 position:30% line:83% align:start
Go up the field
and take us to the finals!

00:09:10.017 --> 00:09:10.718 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:11.318 --> 00:09:12.253 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's what I will do.

00:09:12.286 --> 00:09:14.188 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's time to counterattack.

00:09:14.221 --> 00:09:16.157 position:13% line:89% align:start
We have to go back quickly.

00:09:16.190 --> 00:09:18.192 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah! Come on!

00:09:19.528 --> 00:09:21.530 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa</i>
 <i>runs at great speed</i>

00:09:21.562 --> 00:09:22.663 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>towards</i>
 <i>the opponent's goal.</i>

00:09:22.696 --> 00:09:24.131 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>last play.</i>

00:09:24.165 --> 00:09:24.899 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Come on,
-Yeah!

00:09:24.932 --> 00:09:26.767 position:16% line:83% align:start
-you can do it, Tsubasa!
-Come on!

00:09:26.801 --> 00:09:29.904 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>Ishizaki sacrificed himself</i>
 <i>for this opportunity</i>

00:09:29.937 --> 00:09:32.306 position:10% line:83% align:start
-We have to catch up to him.
-Yeah, Brother.

00:09:32.339 --> 00:09:33.074 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mamoru!

00:09:33.874 --> 00:09:35.242 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa</i>
 <i>makes a pass</i>

00:09:35.276 --> 00:09:36.410 position:33% line:83% align:start
- <i>for Izawa.</i>
-[panting]

00:09:36.444 --> 00:09:38.646 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>And he keeps</i>
 <i>running ahead.</i>

00:09:38.679 --> 00:09:40.648 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Hanawa's defense</i>
 <i>is looking shaky,</i>

00:09:40.681 --> 00:09:43.417 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>even if they are set</i>
 <i>on stopping him.</i>

00:09:43.451 --> 00:09:44.652 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:09:44.685 --> 00:09:47.388 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Mamoru Izawa</i>
 <i>kicks a crossover pass.</i>

00:09:47.421 --> 00:09:48.789 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>And Tsubasa has it.</i>

00:09:48.823 --> 00:09:49.890 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's right on front</i>
 <i>of the goal.</i>

00:09:49.924 --> 00:09:51.192 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Will he get closer</i>
 <i>to shoot,</i>

00:09:51.225 --> 00:09:52.026 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>or will he try to shoot from</i>

00:09:52.059 --> 00:09:53.727 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>the outside of</i>
 <i>the danger zone?</i>

00:09:53.761 --> 00:09:55.963 position:16% line:83% align:start
Will he attempt to shoot
the Drive Shot again?

00:09:57.098 --> 00:09:58.866 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>If I miss this shot now...</i>

00:09:58.899 --> 00:10:02.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Ishizaki's sacrifice</i>
 <i>will be for nothing.</i>

00:10:02.537 --> 00:10:04.138 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have to ignore the pain.</i>

00:10:05.139 --> 00:10:06.640 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>And give it my all!</i>

00:10:06.674 --> 00:10:08.309 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa decides</i>
 <i>not to shoot</i>

00:10:08.342 --> 00:10:09.877 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and goes inside</i>
 <i>the danger zone.</i>

00:10:09.910 --> 00:10:11.479 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everything will be</i>
 <i>decided here.</i>

00:10:11.513 --> 00:10:12.613 position:27% line:89% align:start
Careful, Tsubasa.

00:10:12.646 --> 00:10:13.747 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's that boy up to?

00:10:13.781 --> 00:10:14.715 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Guys, stop him!
-Don't let him

00:10:14.748 --> 00:10:15.616 position:30% line:89% align:start
make the shot.

00:10:15.649 --> 00:10:17.184 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have to shake them off me.</i>

00:10:17.218 --> 00:10:18.919 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[grunt]

00:10:18.953 --> 00:10:19.920 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:10:19.954 --> 00:10:21.722 position:13% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa gets through</i>
 <i>two defenders.</i>

00:10:21.755 --> 00:10:22.723 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>He's shaking off</i>

00:10:22.756 --> 00:10:24.191 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>the defense by himself.</i>
-[gasps]

00:10:24.225 --> 00:10:25.726 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:10:25.759 --> 00:10:26.627 position:35% line:83% align:start
- <i>I did it.</i>
-[grunt]

00:10:26.660 --> 00:10:28.395 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>No! Who's that?</i>
-[grunt]

00:10:28.429 --> 00:10:29.730 position:27% line:83% align:start
-You won't score!
-[grunt]

00:10:29.763 --> 00:10:31.533 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But Team Hanawa</i>
 <i>won't give up.</i>

00:10:31.566 --> 00:10:33.033 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>They'll fight</i>
 <i>tooth and nail</i>

00:10:33.067 --> 00:10:34.135 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>until the end.</i>

00:10:34.168 --> 00:10:35.002 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:10:35.035 --> 00:10:37.771 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa loses</i>
 <i>his balance.</i>

00:10:37.805 --> 00:10:39.173 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, the ball's mine!

00:10:39.206 --> 00:10:40.641 position:19% line:89% align:start
As if I'd ever let you!

00:10:41.375 --> 00:10:42.643 position:35% line:89% align:start
Impossible!

00:10:43.043 --> 00:10:43.944 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:10:43.978 --> 00:10:44.979 position:41% line:89% align:start
[wince]

00:10:45.012 --> 00:10:45.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
No, my shoulder!

00:10:45.746 --> 00:10:47.014 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
It's mine!

00:10:47.047 --> 00:10:48.115 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Hanawa's</i>
 <i>goalkeeper</i>

00:10:48.149 --> 00:10:50.651 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>leaves the goal</i>
 <i>to go get the ball.</i>

00:10:50.684 --> 00:10:53.053 position:16% line:83% align:start
[pant] We have to protect
the goal, Brother.

00:10:53.087 --> 00:10:54.288 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:10:54.321 --> 00:10:55.756 position:21% line:83% align:start
I am Team Nankatsu's
captain.

00:10:55.789 --> 00:10:58.159 position:13% line:83% align:start
I can't just let some pain
stop me from scoring.

00:10:58.192 --> 00:10:59.894 position:19% line:89% align:start
I have to make a goal.

00:11:01.061 --> 00:11:02.763 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>The goalkeeper dives,</i>

00:11:02.796 --> 00:11:04.064 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>but Tsubasa slide tackles</i>

00:11:04.098 --> 00:11:05.799 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and manages to</i>
 <i>kick the ball</i>

00:11:05.833 --> 00:11:07.502 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>straight towards</i>
 <i>the goal.</i>

00:11:07.536 --> 00:11:08.969 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-There it is!

00:11:09.003 --> 00:11:10.671 position:24% line:83% align:start
-It's not over yet!
-It's not over yet!

00:11:10.704 --> 00:11:12.541 position:27% line:89% align:start
Skylab Hurricane!

00:11:12.574 --> 00:11:13.707 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:11:13.741 --> 00:11:15.843 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The twins use</i>
 <i>their special move</i>

00:11:15.876 --> 00:11:17.344 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>to protect the goal.</i>

00:11:17.378 --> 00:11:20.314 position:13% line:83% align:start
If they manage to block it,
it's gonna be all over.

00:11:20.347 --> 00:11:21.882 position:19% line:89% align:start
We won't let you score!

00:11:21.916 --> 00:11:23.450 position:30% line:83% align:start
-What happened?
-What happened?

00:11:23.484 --> 00:11:24.351 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:11:25.319 --> 00:11:27.589 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>But they weren't</i>
 <i>able to reach it</i>

00:11:27.622 --> 00:11:29.089 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the ball</i>
 <i>hits the net.</i>

00:11:29.123 --> 00:11:31.926 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu is winning</i>
 <i>by a goal.</i>

00:11:31.959 --> 00:11:33.027 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:33.060 --> 00:11:33.727 position:27% line:89% align:start
I really did it.

00:11:33.761 --> 00:11:34.695 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:11:34.728 --> 00:11:36.697 position:38% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa,
you're so awesome.

00:11:36.730 --> 00:11:38.232 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Good job, Tsubasa!

00:11:38.265 --> 00:11:39.099 position:27% line:89% align:start
He really did it!

00:11:39.133 --> 00:11:40.935 position:35% line:83% align:start
Well, yeah,
he better have made that.

00:11:40.968 --> 00:11:43.572 position:21% line:83% align:start
I didn't hit my head
for him to miss.

00:11:43.605 --> 00:11:46.407 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh, that boy never
listens to me, does he?

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:49.944 position:10% line:83% align:start
Guess I have no other choice
but to patch him up again.

00:11:49.977 --> 00:11:50.811 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:11:50.844 --> 00:11:53.582 position:16% line:83% align:start
No! We were so damn close
to winning!

00:11:53.615 --> 00:11:54.516 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:54.549 --> 00:11:55.716 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[sobs]
-[ann] <i>Team Hanawa</i>

00:11:55.749 --> 00:11:58.485 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>is stunned from what</i>
 <i>they just witnessed.</i>

00:11:58.520 --> 00:11:59.720 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:11:59.753 --> 00:12:02.723 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And it's done, everyone.</i>
 <i>Team Nankatsu wins.</i>

00:12:02.756 --> 00:12:04.258 position:16% line:83% align:start
-We won the match, guys!
-[applause]

00:12:04.291 --> 00:12:06.026 position:24% line:83% align:start
And now we're on to
the next phase.

00:12:06.060 --> 00:12:07.394 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[groan]
-[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>

00:12:07.428 --> 00:12:09.863 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>shows why they're one of</i>
 <i>the tournament's favorites.</i>

00:12:09.897 --> 00:12:11.799 position:21% line:89% align:start
Once again, we lose.

00:12:12.701 --> 00:12:15.035 position:30% line:83% align:start
The Nankatsu is
a very strong team.

00:12:15.069 --> 00:12:17.706 position:16% line:83% align:start
Stronger than I gave them
credit for.

00:12:17.738 --> 00:12:20.374 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The crowd applauds</i>
 <i>and cheers both teams</i>

00:12:20.407 --> 00:12:21.676 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>for their great effort.</i>

00:12:21.710 --> 00:12:23.545 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even though</i>
 <i>Hanawa lost,</i>

00:12:23.578 --> 00:12:24.745 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>everyone recognizes</i>

00:12:24.778 --> 00:12:26.413 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>their magnificent</i>
 <i>resilience.</i>

00:12:26.447 --> 00:12:28.683 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>
 <i>this match was at</i>

00:12:28.717 --> 00:12:30.951 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>a finals' level</i>
 <i>of gameplay.</i>

00:12:31.885 --> 00:12:34.755 position:21% line:83% align:start
Effort means nothing
if you don't win.

00:12:35.889 --> 00:12:38.926 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'll wait for you
in the finals, Tsubasa.

00:12:38.959 --> 00:12:42.263 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll see who's better
between the two of us now.

00:12:45.099 --> 00:12:47.602 position:33% line:83% align:start
Hello, Hyuga.
How are you?

00:12:47.636 --> 00:12:49.069 position:33% line:89% align:start
Matsuyama...

00:12:50.605 --> 00:12:53.240 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>We'll be right back</i>
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:12:56.910 --> 00:12:58.445 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>And we're back.</i>

00:13:01.683 --> 00:13:02.617 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Infirmary.</i>

00:13:02.651 --> 00:13:03.951 position:38% line:83% align:start
[doctor]
Would you look at that...

00:13:03.984 --> 00:13:04.852 position:21% line:89% align:start
What did I tell you?

00:13:04.885 --> 00:13:06.588 position:13% line:89% align:start
And yet, you still did it.

00:13:06.621 --> 00:13:08.022 position:24% line:89% align:start
Foolish little boy.

00:13:08.055 --> 00:13:09.456 position:41% line:89% align:start
[laugh]

00:13:09.490 --> 00:13:10.558 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, doctor.

00:13:10.592 --> 00:13:12.493 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's just that
I got carried away.

00:13:12.527 --> 00:13:13.762 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[scream] That hurts.
-[grunt]

00:13:13.794 --> 00:13:15.296 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh no, is it hurting a lot?

00:13:15.329 --> 00:13:16.196 position:35% line:89% align:start
Captain...

00:13:16.230 --> 00:13:18.132 position:21% line:83% align:start
Is it hurting a lot?
Are you okay?

00:13:18.165 --> 00:13:19.567 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:13:19.601 --> 00:13:20.568 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait!

00:13:20.602 --> 00:13:22.269 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why's everyone worried
about him?

00:13:22.303 --> 00:13:24.138 position:21% line:83% align:start
I hit my fragile head
and no one's worried.

00:13:24.171 --> 00:13:25.973 position:24% line:83% align:start
You've always been
the strong one.

00:13:26.006 --> 00:13:27.374 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why do you want us
to worry?

00:13:27.408 --> 00:13:30.110 position:24% line:83% align:start
-I really hate you.
-Aw, come on, don't get mad.

00:13:30.144 --> 00:13:33.080 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:13:33.881 --> 00:13:34.982 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:13:35.015 --> 00:13:37.084 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hello, Tsubasa,
how's your injury doing?

00:13:37.117 --> 00:13:38.919 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hajime]
It's the Tachibana Twins.

00:13:38.952 --> 00:13:40.555 position:27% line:89% align:start
Kazuo and Masao.

00:13:40.588 --> 00:13:42.089 position:30% line:83% align:start
It was my fault
you're injured,

00:13:42.122 --> 00:13:44.325 position:30% line:83% align:start
so I came here
to apologize to you.

00:13:44.358 --> 00:13:45.159 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, it's fine.

00:13:45.192 --> 00:13:46.927 position:27% line:83% align:start
You have nothing
to worry about, pal.

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:49.798 position:16% line:83% align:start
What's important is that
you're okay.

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:50.964 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Oh...
-Oh...

00:13:50.998 --> 00:13:53.067 position:13% line:83% align:start
By the way, congratulations
to the vulture

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:54.902 position:33% line:83% align:start
who deflected
our game winning shot.

00:13:54.935 --> 00:13:55.969 position:21% line:89% align:start
It was a great dive.

00:13:56.003 --> 00:13:57.739 position:24% line:83% align:start
Who are you calling
a vulture?

00:13:57.772 --> 00:13:58.872 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-You're so rude to me.

00:13:58.906 --> 00:14:00.742 position:24% line:89% align:start
No one respects me.

00:14:00.775 --> 00:14:02.443 position:24% line:83% align:start
Win the tournament
on our behalf.

00:14:02.476 --> 00:14:04.912 position:16% line:83% align:start
We'll be cheering you on
from the sidelines.

00:14:04.945 --> 00:14:05.979 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can count on us.

00:14:06.013 --> 00:14:08.349 position:38% line:83% align:start
We'll win
our third championship.

00:14:08.382 --> 00:14:10.150 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-[Ryo] Yeah!

00:14:10.884 --> 00:14:12.052 position:38% line:89% align:start
[beeping]

00:14:13.087 --> 00:14:15.824 position:24% line:83% align:start
By the looks of it,
you were never injured.

00:14:15.856 --> 00:14:18.459 position:16% line:83% align:start
I wasn't. The coach just
said that to the media.

00:14:18.492 --> 00:14:20.928 position:27% line:83% align:start
So then tell me,
why aren't you on the pitch?

00:14:20.961 --> 00:14:22.196 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, but um,

00:14:22.229 --> 00:14:24.331 position:30% line:83% align:start
that is none of
your concern.

00:14:24.365 --> 00:14:26.166 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[drinking]
-Of course it is, Hyuga.

00:14:26.200 --> 00:14:28.603 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have a pending issue
to resolve.

00:14:28.636 --> 00:14:30.705 position:13% line:89% align:start
Or did you forget about it?

00:14:30.739 --> 00:14:32.106 position:13% line:89% align:start
We have a score to settle.

00:14:32.139 --> 00:14:34.576 position:21% line:83% align:start
You hit me back when
we were in elementary.

00:14:35.943 --> 00:14:37.478 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
That was a long time ago.

00:14:37.512 --> 00:14:38.445 position:33% line:89% align:start
Get over it.

00:14:38.479 --> 00:14:41.181 position:24% line:83% align:start
We will be the ones
to take out Nankatsu,

00:14:41.215 --> 00:14:42.650 position:13% line:89% align:start
and then it'll be all over

00:14:42.684 --> 00:14:44.017 position:19% line:83% align:start
for you and your team,
Hyuga.

00:14:44.051 --> 00:14:45.185 position:19% line:89% align:start
You had better be ready

00:14:45.219 --> 00:14:47.522 position:19% line:83% align:start
because I'll pummel you
in the finals.

00:14:48.656 --> 00:14:50.558 position:16% line:83% align:start
That's all I have to say
to you.

00:14:52.126 --> 00:14:53.127 position:38% line:89% align:start
Goodbye.

00:14:55.462 --> 00:14:56.463 position:41% line:89% align:start
[smirk]

00:14:58.232 --> 00:15:00.901 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Furuoya] Everybody,
get back on the bus.

00:15:00.934 --> 00:15:02.903 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Man, that was a good match.

00:15:02.936 --> 00:15:04.905 position:27% line:83% align:start
[sigh] Can't wait
to go home, though.

00:15:04.938 --> 00:15:06.508 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
Look, it's Hyuga.

00:15:06.541 --> 00:15:08.075 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hyuga?
-Huh?

00:15:08.777 --> 00:15:09.977 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[Ryo] Hey, Hyuga!

00:15:10.010 --> 00:15:10.944 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[Kojiro] Oh!
-What're you doing

00:15:10.978 --> 00:15:11.912 position:35% line:89% align:start
over there?

00:15:11.945 --> 00:15:13.947 position:30% line:83% align:start
Didn't you have
a match today?

00:15:13.981 --> 00:15:15.884 position:27% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't be
leaving your teammates

00:15:15.916 --> 00:15:17.284 position:30% line:89% align:start
by themselves.

00:15:17.317 --> 00:15:18.553 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you worry.

00:15:18.586 --> 00:15:20.722 position:16% line:83% align:start
They don't need me to win
such an easy match

00:15:20.755 --> 00:15:21.890 position:21% line:89% align:start
against a weak team.

00:15:21.922 --> 00:15:22.990 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, Hyuga,

00:15:23.023 --> 00:15:24.425 position:13% line:83% align:start
you're not really injured,
are you?

00:15:24.458 --> 00:15:26.193 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh... No.

00:15:26.226 --> 00:15:28.095 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's not like I have
an option, Hyuga.

00:15:28.128 --> 00:15:30.030 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll just have to anxiously
wait for the finals

00:15:30.063 --> 00:15:31.365 position:21% line:89% align:start
to go up against you.

00:15:31.398 --> 00:15:33.133 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-[chuckle]

00:15:33.967 --> 00:15:35.102 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:15:35.135 --> 00:15:37.070 position:16% line:83% align:start
[reac] You had better be
in perfect condition

00:15:37.104 --> 00:15:38.939 position:27% line:89% align:start
by then, Tsubasa!

00:15:38.972 --> 00:15:41.609 position:16% line:83% align:start
Because I will defeat you
no matter what.

00:15:42.911 --> 00:15:44.111 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:15:45.979 --> 00:15:48.550 position:21% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>16th National</i>
 <i>Middle School Tournament.</i>

00:15:48.583 --> 00:15:50.785 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:15:50.819 --> 00:15:52.085 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>And the referee whistles</i>

00:15:52.119 --> 00:15:53.555 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>the end of the match.</i>

00:15:53.588 --> 00:15:55.989 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Toho Academy utterly</i>
 <i>defeats Team Myoko</i>

00:15:56.023 --> 00:15:57.792 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>by a 3 to nil margin,</i>

00:15:57.826 --> 00:15:59.026 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and with this,</i>
 <i>they pave their way</i>

00:15:59.059 --> 00:16:00.895 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>to the next round.</i>

00:16:00.929 --> 00:16:01.930 position:24% line:89% align:start
We did it, Captain.

00:16:01.962 --> 00:16:03.163 position:35% line:89% align:start
We did it.

00:16:06.467 --> 00:16:10.905 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:16:10.939 --> 00:16:12.072 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm open, Captain.

00:16:12.105 --> 00:16:13.173 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, Big Brother.

00:16:14.007 --> 00:16:15.510 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hello.
-Good afternoon, Hyuga.

00:16:15.543 --> 00:16:17.344 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're your friends,
right, Big Brother?

00:16:17.377 --> 00:16:19.112 position:16% line:83% align:start
We were just playing ball
for a bit.

00:16:19.146 --> 00:16:20.548 position:19% line:89% align:start
What're you doing here?

00:16:20.582 --> 00:16:22.349 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did you come to make
fun of my house, Prince?

00:16:22.382 --> 00:16:23.551 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:16:23.585 --> 00:16:26.420 position:10% line:83% align:start
You didn't play in the match
with your teammates, Hyuga.

00:16:26.453 --> 00:16:26.754 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:16:27.822 --> 00:16:29.657 position:24% line:83% align:start
I was just talking
with your mother.

00:16:29.691 --> 00:16:30.991 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tell me, what's going on
with you?

00:16:31.024 --> 00:16:32.961 position:21% line:83% align:start
Are you really trying
to hide something?

00:16:32.993 --> 00:16:34.061 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Spill it.
-Misugi,

00:16:34.094 --> 00:16:35.429 position:13% line:89% align:start
get straight to the point.

00:16:36.129 --> 00:16:37.799 position:21% line:89% align:start
Listen to me well...

00:16:37.832 --> 00:16:39.901 position:35% line:83% align:start
You beat us
out on the pitch.

00:16:39.934 --> 00:16:41.970 position:24% line:83% align:start
Your responsibility
is to represent

00:16:42.002 --> 00:16:45.072 position:27% line:83% align:start
the city of Tokyo
in the national tournament.

00:16:45.105 --> 00:16:46.473 position:21% line:89% align:start
And for that reason,

00:16:46.508 --> 00:16:49.611 position:10% line:83% align:start
I will not allow you to lose
to a mediocre team

00:16:49.644 --> 00:16:50.845 position:10% line:89% align:start
simply because you felt like

00:16:50.879 --> 00:16:52.814 position:30% line:83% align:start
not showing up
to a match, Hyuga.

00:16:52.847 --> 00:16:54.616 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's unacceptable.

00:16:54.649 --> 00:16:55.650 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:17:00.855 --> 00:17:02.055 position:33% line:83% align:start
If that's all
you had to say,

00:17:02.089 --> 00:17:03.123 position:30% line:89% align:start
you can leave.

00:17:03.156 --> 00:17:05.025 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-But Big Brother...

00:17:05.058 --> 00:17:06.159 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:17:06.628 --> 00:17:07.562 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's get going.

00:17:07.595 --> 00:17:09.129 position:38% line:83% align:start
Oh, uh...
Yeah, Captain.

00:17:11.365 --> 00:17:14.669 position:19% line:83% align:start
I can clearly tell that
you've gotten stronger.

00:17:14.702 --> 00:17:15.703 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're not injured.

00:17:16.738 --> 00:17:20.073 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're the only one
who can defeat Tsubasa.

00:17:20.107 --> 00:17:22.877 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll be anxiously waiting
for that great final.

00:17:22.911 --> 00:17:24.444 position:21% line:83% align:start
-You take care, okay?
-Mhm.

00:17:27.047 --> 00:17:28.248 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:17:29.349 --> 00:17:30.919 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I don't understand</i>
 <i>why everyone</i>

00:17:30.952 --> 00:17:33.955 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>is always set on being</i>
 <i>in my business.</i>

00:17:33.988 --> 00:17:35.188 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:17:35.924 --> 00:17:37.324 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Wait, Big Brother!
-Takeru!

00:17:37.357 --> 00:17:38.191 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uhh...

00:17:38.225 --> 00:17:40.929 position:10% line:83% align:start
Don't let this happen again,
you hear?

00:17:40.962 --> 00:17:42.062 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>You'll see.</i>

00:17:42.095 --> 00:17:43.665 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll show everyone...</i>

00:17:43.698 --> 00:17:46.466 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>that I'm the best player</i>
 <i>in the tournament.</i>

00:17:51.973 --> 00:17:53.908 position:30% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>And so,</i>
 <i>the fifth day of</i>

00:17:53.942 --> 00:17:55.610 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>the National Tournament</i>
 <i>arrived</i>

00:17:55.643 --> 00:17:58.445 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the next phase</i>
 <i>is about to begin.</i>

00:17:59.413 --> 00:18:02.016 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>From Block A,</i>
 <i>we have Team Nankatsu,</i>

00:18:02.050 --> 00:18:03.685 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>representing Shizuoka.</i>

00:18:03.718 --> 00:18:06.453 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>And Team Hirado</i>
 <i>representing Nagasaki,</i>

00:18:06.486 --> 00:18:07.354 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Team Minami-Uwa,</i>

00:18:07.387 --> 00:18:09.189 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>representing</i>
 <i>Ehime prefecture</i>

00:18:09.222 --> 00:18:11.960 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Team Furano</i>
 <i>representing Hokkaido.</i>

00:18:11.993 --> 00:18:13.928 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>In Block B,</i>
 <i>we have Toho Academy,</i>

00:18:13.962 --> 00:18:15.262 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>representing Tokyo,</i>

00:18:15.295 --> 00:18:17.532 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Chubu</i>
 <i>representing Nagano,</i>

00:18:17.565 --> 00:18:20.100 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Meiwa</i>
 <i>representing Saitama,</i>

00:18:20.133 --> 00:18:22.737 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Team Kanamura</i>
 <i>representing Miyazaki.</i>

00:18:33.781 --> 00:18:34.716 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:34.749 --> 00:18:36.918 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[Takeshi] Captain Hyuga!
-[Kazuki] Captain!

00:18:36.951 --> 00:18:38.086 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hello, Coach.

00:18:38.118 --> 00:18:40.054 position:19% line:83% align:start
Today, I'll be sitting
on the bench.

00:18:40.088 --> 00:18:41.556 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-[chuckle]

00:18:41.589 --> 00:18:43.758 position:33% line:83% align:start
I see you're
as stubborn as ever.

00:18:44.993 --> 00:18:48.029 position:33% line:83% align:start
Well, you are
a Toho Academy player.

00:18:48.062 --> 00:18:50.364 position:16% line:83% align:start
You can hang around here
if you'd like.

00:18:50.397 --> 00:18:52.199 position:24% line:83% align:start
But you won't play,
you understand?

00:18:52.232 --> 00:18:53.668 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:18:53.701 --> 00:18:54.569 position:24% line:89% align:start
You know damn well

00:18:54.602 --> 00:18:56.504 position:35% line:83% align:start
you need me
to win this match.

00:19:00.608 --> 00:19:02.777 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:19:02.810 --> 00:19:05.379 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And there it is,</i>
 <i>the end of the match.</i>

00:19:05.412 --> 00:19:07.081 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Meiwa</i>
 <i>finally defeats</i>

00:19:07.115 --> 00:19:08.716 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Kanamura,</i>
 <i>2 to nothing.</i>

00:19:08.750 --> 00:19:10.450 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>And so, they've earned</i>
 <i>their place</i>

00:19:10.484 --> 00:19:13.121 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>as the first semifinalist</i>
 <i>of the tournament.</i>

00:19:13.186 --> 00:19:15.056 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>This was</i>
 <i>an incredible match.</i>

00:19:15.089 --> 00:19:16.557 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>See you</i>
 <i>in the semifinals.</i>

00:19:16.591 --> 00:19:18.926 position:24% line:83% align:start
Team Meiwa made it
to the semifinals.

00:19:18.960 --> 00:19:19.961 position:24% line:89% align:start
Even without Hyuga,

00:19:19.994 --> 00:19:21.361 position:33% line:83% align:start
they're still
a very strong team.

00:19:21.395 --> 00:19:22.329 position:38% line:89% align:start
Exactly.

00:19:22.362 --> 00:19:23.965 position:13% line:89% align:start
It'll be interesting to see

00:19:23.998 --> 00:19:27.502 position:27% line:83% align:start
which are the 24
most value players.

00:19:27.535 --> 00:19:29.937 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll choose</i>
 <i>the best 24 players</i>

00:19:29.971 --> 00:19:31.072 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>from this tournament,</i>

00:19:31.105 --> 00:19:33.908 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and give them</i>
 <i>an intensive training.</i>

00:19:33.941 --> 00:19:34.709 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>And then...</i>

00:19:35.409 --> 00:19:37.078 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll send them to Europe,</i>

00:19:37.111 --> 00:19:40.313 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>so they can prove</i>
 <i>their skills in soccer.</i>

00:19:41.783 --> 00:19:43.651 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now let me see your foot.

00:19:43.685 --> 00:19:44.919 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Tsubasa...

00:19:44.952 --> 00:19:46.954 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't you dare
play dumb with me.

00:19:46.988 --> 00:19:48.756 position:10% line:89% align:start
You can't fool this old man.

00:19:48.790 --> 00:19:50.457 position:10% line:89% align:start
I know your foot is injured.

00:19:50.490 --> 00:19:51.993 position:13% line:89% align:start
Doctor, I swear it's fine.

00:19:52.026 --> 00:19:53.961 position:24% line:83% align:start
Stop being stubborn
and let me see it.

00:19:53.995 --> 00:19:55.129 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:19:55.163 --> 00:19:57.098 position:16% line:83% align:start
I see you already had it
wrapped, young man.

00:19:57.131 --> 00:19:58.365 position:35% line:89% align:start
I told you.

00:19:58.700 --> 00:19:59.399 position:41% line:89% align:start
And...

00:19:59.433 --> 00:20:01.069 position:19% line:83% align:start
it's a superb wrapping
at that.

00:20:01.102 --> 00:20:03.004 position:38% line:83% align:start
Tell me,
was it your dear manager

00:20:03.037 --> 00:20:04.237 position:27% line:89% align:start
or someone else?

00:20:04.271 --> 00:20:06.974 position:44% line:83% align:start
Um...
I think it was...

00:20:07.008 --> 00:20:08.943 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you mean
you think, young man?

00:20:08.976 --> 00:20:09.944 position:38% line:89% align:start
