00:21:01.162 --> 00:21:02.063 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
[chuckle]

00:21:02.096 --> 00:21:03.296 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:21:04.431 --> 00:21:06.134 position:44% line:83% align:start
