00:21:22.617 --> 00:21:25.019 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:21:26.654 --> 00:21:27.855 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uhh...

00:21:28.923 --> 00:21:31.526 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, I'm hoping for
a good match, Captain.

00:21:31.559 --> 00:21:32.560 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:21:33.027 --> 00:21:33.961 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:21:33.995 --> 00:21:35.362 position:41% line:89% align:start
