00:21:45.106 --> 00:21:46.306 position:41% line:89% align:start
[smirk]

00:21:47.041 --> 00:21:48.976 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's Kojiro Hyuga...

00:21:49.010 --> 00:21:50.211 position:24% line:89% align:start
I can't believe it.

00:21:50.244 --> 00:21:52.113 position:13% line:83% align:start
-This just got interesting.
-Wow!

00:21:52.146 --> 00:21:53.948 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now their team's
finally complete.

00:21:55.149 --> 00:21:55.983 position:35% line:89% align:start
Keep it up.

00:21:56.017 --> 00:21:57.251 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain.

00:21:57.285 --> 00:21:58.485 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

