 <i>play in this match.</i>

00:22:03.057 --> 00:22:04.357 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>But that doesn't matter.</i>

00:22:05.560 --> 00:22:09.630 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>They know they can't win</i>
 <i>the final match without me.</i>

00:22:09.664 --> 00:22:12.066 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>For now,</i>
 <i>I need to have discipline.</i>

00:22:12.099 --> 00:22:13.801 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't cause any problems.</i>

00:22:13.835 --> 00:22:15.870 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I just have to trust</i>
 <i>my teammates,</i>

00:22:15.903 --> 00:22:18.172 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>but I guess I can</i>
 <i>help them a bit.</i>

00:22:18.206 --> 00:22:19.674 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>And when we get to</i>
 <i>the finals,</i>

00:22:19.707 --> 00:22:21.742 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>they'll know</i>
 <i>my true strength.</i>

00:22:24.312 --> 00:22:25.246 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:22:25.279 --> 00:22:26.814 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>What a powerful kick.</i>

00:22:26.848 --> 00:22:30.051 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>His strength's grown</i>
 <i>since last year.</i>

00:22:30.084 --> 00:22:34.088 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Just like I imagined,</i>
 <i>Hyuga was never injured.</i>

00:22:34.121 --> 00:22:35.990 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro]
 <i>I will be the one...</i>

00:22:36.023 --> 00:22:37.925 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>to win this tournament.</i>

